## EXAMPLE ATTRIBUTION

When distributing or modifying this software, include attribution like:

### ✅ CORRECT ATTRIBUTION:

```
paramEXT - Enhanced SyncShare
Based on SyncShare by Naloaty
https://github.com/yourname/paramEXT

This software is based on SyncShare 
(https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/syncshare/lngijbnmdkejbgnkakeiapeppbpaapib)
and includes the following modifications:
- Auto-Insert mode for automatic answer filling
- Auto-Solve mode for automatic test completion
- Enhanced error handling

Released under MIT License with Attribution.
See LICENSE file for full details.
```

### ❌ INCORRECT ATTRIBUTION:

```
❌ "paramEXT - My Original Extension"
❌ "SyncShare Enhanced Edition"
❌ "My Super Smart Quiz Solver"
(without mentioning SyncShare or paramEXT)
```

